\implies a_na_{n+2}a_{n+4}>0\ \forall\ \text{n is odd}
\implies \prod\limits^{2n+1}_{k=1}a_n>0\ \forall\ n$.
Also, $a_na_{n+1}=2^{1/19}\frac{1}{2^{1/36}}=2^{1/12}$ does not depend on $n$.
